OL,3,CPolice investigate after child
OL,4,Cbelieved to have fallen from window
OL,6,FA police cordon is in place on a
OL,7,FMiddlesbrough street after a child is
OL,8,Fbelieved to have fallen from a window.
OL,10,FThe incident is said to have occurred
OL,11,Fat a property on Palmer Street shortly
OL,12,Fbefore 5pm yesterday evening (Thursday
OL,13,F2 April).
OL,15,FThe patient was taken to James Cook
OL,16,FHospital for further treatment where
OL,17,Fthey remain in a serious but stable
OL,18,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
