OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775239864
OL,3,CPolice investigate after child
OL,4,Cbelieved to have fallen from window
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Rebecca Taylor,
OL,7,Ffrom Cleveland Police's Protecting
OL,8,FVulnerable People team, said: "Shortly
OL,9,Fbefore 5pm on Thursday 2 April police
OL,10,Fwere called to Palmer Street in
OL,11,FMiddlesbrough following concerns for a
OL,12,Fchild who was reported to have fallen
OL,13,Ffrom the window of a property.
OL,15,F"Paramedics attended and provided
OL,16,Ftreatment to the child who was taken
OL,17,Fto hospital where he is in a serious
OL,18,Fbut stable condition."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
