OL,3,CPolice investigate after child
OL,4,Cbelieved to have fallen from window
OL,6,FA North East Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We received a call
OL,8,Fat 4.46pm on Thursday 2 April to
OL,9,Freports of a person injured on Palmer
OL,10,FStreet in Middlesbrough.
OL,12,F"We dispatched an ambulance crew and a
OL,13,Fclinical team leader to the scene, and
OL,14,Ftransported one patient to James Cook
OL,15,Fhospital for further treatment."
OL,17,FPolice are asking anyone with
OL,18,Finformation, CCTV or doorbell footage
OL,19,Fto contact them on 101 or visit the
OL,20,Fwebsite quoting reference number
OL,21,F061391.
